high_descs: Turn around to reach the larger sofa on the right of the table.
Pick up the spoon from the couch.
Turn around to reach the cup on the shelf.
Put the spoon in the cup on the shelf.
Pick up the cup from the shelf.
Turn around to reach the sidetable.
Put the cup on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the Spoon with the Cup on the SideTable.

high_descs: Go to the sofa.
Take the spoon.
Turn around and go to the cup shelf.
Place the spoon in the cup.
Take the cup with the spoon.
Return to the sidetable.
Place the cup with the spoon on the left sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Find a spoon and a cup and place them on the side table.

high_descs: Turn towards your left and again turn left then move towards the sofa.
Take a silver spoon from the couch.
Turn left and again turn left one more time and move towards the cup rack.
Place the spoon in the cup.
Take the cup in hand.
Turn left and once again turn towards your left and head towards the sidetable.
Place the cup on the left side of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the spoon and cup on the side table.
